    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> It was my initial proposal but since I wanted it to be applied on all facets and not for each facet, it was kind of confusing.\n\nOhhh I did not see it. Maybe we could right now try to find a good name where we are able to reformat the whole data (and thus handle both map, filter, reduce..)\n",
