    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "We are most probably going for templates being only functions, thus the need to reformat the whole data can be handled in the templating system. Then it will be our job to educate on how to keep using mustache while being able to reformat the data.\n\nBecause once you use formatData what you want to do is change the template to add more data or filter it.\n\nI will revisit this one once settled on the template situation.\n",
